highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Kolkata. “Kesariya” is the highest at #4.
“Raabta” by Pritam and Arijit Singh is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Kolkata, up 44 spots at #37.
“Tu Aake Dekhle” by King has been on Top Songs Kolkata the longest, at 67 weeks straight.
“KALESHI CHORI” by DG IMMORTALS, Raga, Harjas Harjaayi, VIRTUAL_AF, and DARK HORSE is the highest new entry on Top Songs Kolkata at #92.
